ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Seminar course for all students, staff, and faculty organized in the Organic Chemistry division. Yes.
Different lectures about new and important discoveries around the world.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Exposure to ongoing research by others is critical to further one's education in the subject material and "stay on top of the game" as one pursues their own research efforts.
It was helpful to learn about the various fascinating research being done in the broad field of organic chemistry.
